<P>
   BEIRUT _ The Kurds' most radical leader, Abdullah Ocalan _ whose
capture Tuesday set off a wave of simultaneous embassy takeovers
throughout Europe _ is, even in many Kurdish eyes, a psychopathic
killer. Ocalan is no political innocent, no abider by human rights,
no Robin Hood... &QL;
</P>
