<HEADLINE>
`HOMICIDE' WEB SITE LINKS FANS TO CYBER PLOT 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Repeating as part of a weekly roundup of computer features)   By PATTI HARTIGAN   
 c.1999 The Boston Globe   
<TEXT>
