percent, and the Nasdaq index was down 1.1 percent. Elsewhere,
prices fell half a percent in Tokyo, while the Hong Kong market
remained closed for a holiday. Shares fell 1.5 percent in Frankfurt
and 0.2 percent in London. They rose 1 percent in Brazil and 0.1
