   Leon International Foods, 4000-A Pleasantdale Road, Doraville,
770-416-6620 (we found orange flower water and couscous here).
</P>
<P>
   It's Tropical, 183 DeKalb Industrial Way, Decatur, 404-377-8075
(a variety of African and Caribbean ingredients).
</P>
<P>
   Afro Mart, 6200 Buford Highway, Norcross, 770-368-0770 (we found
red palm oil here).
</P>
<P>
   Reagan Walker writes for the Atlanta Journal-Constitution.
</P>
