stock market research available on the Internet and thousands of
individuals turning to on-line trading, who needs a stock broker?
asks Business Week in a profile of the investor revolution brought
on by the computer and the Internet. (Walker, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution).
</P>
<P>
   DELL _ Dell shares fall in very heavy trading at midday.
(Mahoney, Austin American-Statesman)
</P>
<P>
   MOTOROLA _Motorola Inc. Wednesday has entered a manufacturing
alliance with Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Co., in which TSMC
will make a wide range of chips for Motorola. This is Motorola's
biggest move toward its goal of outsourcing more of its
manufacturing. (Gallaga, Austin American-Statesman)
</P>
<P>
   TEXAS-SLOGAN _ Texas Department of Economic Development unveils
its new state state tourism campaign - and it's a lot like the old
one. The slogan, in fact, is the same: Texas - It's like a Whole
Other Country. (Austin American-Statesman)
</P>
