<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-17 17:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9026 &Cx1f; taf-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-RENOVATE-ART-2TAKES-N     02-17 1262
