<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-17 17:57 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9089 &Cx1f; ttx-z
r e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-POPMUSIC-FERMAN-TEX     02-17 1292
