<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-DELL-STOCK-NYT </SLUG>
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   EDITORS:
</P>
<P>
   DELL-STOCK (New York) will not move in tonight's New York Times
News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Feb. 17.
