Robertson Stephens, has an inside source at Dell is but one of the
rumors that was circulating on Wall Street Wednesday, one day after
Dell shocked Wall Street by reporting revenues that failed to meet
analysts' estimates. Dell's report was a surprise to everyone but
Niles and the clients of his firm, whom he told on Friday that
