 This ``separate buy'' article is from Latin Trade magazine,
America's leading journal of Latin American business, finance and
trade: &HT;    HOGGING THE LIMELIGHT _ AND AN ACT OF CONGRESS: A TALK WITH
MARIA ROJO. Mexicans are going to movie theaters again, but
Hollywood blockbusters are upstaging the local film industry. And
Maria Rojo's passion has pushed her onto center stage to champion
Mexican film against the overwhelming power of the big-budget
Hollywood movie machine.
