<DOCNO> NYT19990217.0453 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-17 21:05 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9391 &Cx1f; tta-z
