</P>
<P>
   NY-MENS-FASHION (New York) will not move in tonight's New York
Times News Service file.
</P>
<P>
   N.Y.Times News Service, Feb. 17.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-02-17-99 2119EST &QL; 
</TRAILER>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> NYT19990217.0465 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
